  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7657731/" class="title-link">对未来的某种期待。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7657731"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/tobeaway/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u42411454-47.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tobeaway/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">顾八荒。</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-11-13"
      class="main-meta">2015-11-13 17:59:33</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7657731_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  基于我个人的理解，其实赫胥黎在这本书中探讨了两个主题：故事部分着重于无选择的幸福与有选择的不幸的探讨，论述部分着重于诱导术以及虚假宣传对民主力量的破坏。  在美丽新世界里，每个人的命运都毫无差错，一分一厘地扣合着他的属性安排。消费主义盛行，物质充裕；工作都是...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            华东师范大学出版社2014版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7657731_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7657731_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










